  <chunk id="4fa344b02899cb75cb81db82d2cee5f624343c54.c2" text="Methods: GRP78 regulations in HepG2.2.15 cells were conducted by transfections of expressing vector and small interfering RNA, respectively. The changes in HBV replication, hepatitis B e antigen (HBeAg) synthesis and hepatoma cell motility were monitored.">
